 read as follows: “the term ‘depository institution’ means any commercial bank, savings bank, savings and loan association, building and loan association, homestead association (including cooperative banks) or credit union which makes federally related mortgage loans as determined by the Board, mortgage banking subsidiary of a bank holding company or savings and loan holding company, or savings and loan service corporation that originates or purchases mortgage loans;”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Pars. (3) to (6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/73/s1211/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–73, § 1211(e)","children":[],"tail":", added pars. (3) and (4) and redesignated former pars. (3) and (4) as (5) and (6), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1988—Par. (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/242"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–242","children":[],"tail":" struck out “or” before “homestead association” and inserted before semicolon at end “, mortgage banking subsidiary of a bank holding company or savings and loan holding company, or savings and loan service corporation that originates or purchases mortgage loans”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddcf60f42-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"iddcf60f43-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2010 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203","children":[],"tail":" effective on the designated transfer date, see "},{"tag":"ref","at